%F A081039 a(n) = 8*a(n-1) -16*a(n-2) with n>1, a(0)=1, a(1)=7.
%F A081039 a(n) = (3*n+4)*4^(n-1).
%F A081039 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} (k+1)*3^k*binomial(n, k).
%F A081039 G.f.: (1-x)/(1-4*x)^2.
%F A081039 E.g.f.: exp(4*x)*(1 + 3*x). - _Stefano Spezia_, Jan 31 2025
%F A081039 From _Amiram Eldar_, Feb 12 2026: (Start)
%F A081039 Sum_{n>=0} 1/a(n) = (8/3) * (2^(5/3)*sqrt(3)*arctan(sqrt(3)/(1 + 2^(5/3))) - 2^(5/3)*log(2 - 2^(1/3)) + 2^(2/3)*log(4 + 2^(2/3) + 2^(4/3)) - 6).
%F A081039 Sum_{n>=0} (-1)^n/a(n) = (8/3) * (6 - 2^(5/3)*sqrt(3)*(arccot((2^(5/3)-1)/sqrt(3))) - 2^(5/3)*log(2 + 2^(1/3)) + 2^(2/3)*log(4 + 2^(2/3) - 2^(4/3))). (End)
